---
import MainLayout from "../components/MainLayout.astro";

const canonicalPath = "/about";
const title = "About Autonomy Bridge";
const summary =
  "Independent research and advisory on warehouse automation, robotics deployment, and industrial AI.";
---

<MainLayout
  canonicalPath={canonicalPath}
  title={title}
  summary={summary}
  seoTitle="About Autonomy Bridge | Autonomy Bridge"
>
  <article class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto px-6 py-12 md:py-16">
    <header>
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">About Autonomy Bridge</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-8">
        Independent research and advisory on warehouse automation, robotics deployment, and
        industrial AI.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Autonomy Bridge is an independent research and advisory firm focused on warehouse
        automation economics, robotics deployment, and industrial AI adoption.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
        The work is built for operators, investors, and technology teams making decisions under
        real cost, throughput, and deployment constraints. The objective is not to promote
        automation. It is to evaluate where automation holds up, where it fails, and what the
        decision actually requires.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">What the firm does</h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Autonomy Bridge produces structured research, decision frameworks, applied use cases, and
        bespoke analysis for automation and AI infrastructure decisions.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
        The work is designed for questions such as:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-4 text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        <li>whether a deployment can recover capital under actual utilization conditions</li>
        <li>whether a vendor model survives beyond pilot stage</li>
        <li>whether workflow constraints will limit realized ROI</li>
        <li>whether a market entry thesis is credible at the buyer level</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">What the firm is not</h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Autonomy Bridge is not a systems integrator, implementation consultant, staffing firm,
        software reseller, or sponsored research publisher.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
        The firm does not take vendor referral fees, sponsored placements, or paid influence
        arrangements. That boundary exists to preserve analytical independence.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Founder</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[auto,1fr] gap-6 md:gap-8 items-start">
        <div class="w-28 h-28 md:w-36 md:h-36 rounded-md overflow-hidden border border-neutral-200">
          <img
            src="/images/founder/deepak-gupta.jpg?v=20260316b"
            alt="Deepak Gupta"
            class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold mb-1">Deepak Gupta</h3>
          <p class="text-sm uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-neutral-500 mb-4">
            Founder and Principal Analyst
          </p>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
            Deepak Gupta leads Autonomy Bridge. His background spans robotics go-to-market,
            industrial procurement, and commercial development across North America, Europe, and
            Asia-Pacific.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
            He has deep expertise across robotics, SaaS, industrial AI/automation, B2B platforms
            and fintech. That operating exposure informs the firm&rsquo;s research model: decisions
            should be tested against buyer constraints, deployment economics, and execution risk,
            not category narratives.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-2 mt-4 text-sm">
            <a
              href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/deepakgupta5"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="underline underline-offset-4"
            >
              LinkedIn
            </a>
            <a href="/contact" class="underline underline-offset-4">Contact</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">Why this exists</h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        Automation decisions are often made with incomplete economic modeling, optimistic vendor
        assumptions, and weak visibility into failure patterns.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
        Autonomy Bridge exists to close that gap with operator-level analysis. The unit of analysis
        is the actual decision being made: a warehouse investment, a vendor shortlist, a
        pilot-to-scale question, a pricing model, or a market-entry bet.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">
        How the platform is built
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        The platform is structured around permanent analytical assets:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mt-4 text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        <li><a href="/frameworks" class="underline underline-offset-4">frameworks</a></li>
        <li><a href="/glossary" class="underline underline-offset-4">glossary terms</a></li>
        <li><a href="/use-cases" class="underline underline-offset-4">use cases</a></li>
        <li><a href="/case-studies" class="underline underline-offset-4">case studies</a></li>
        <li>
          <a href="/bespoke-research" class="underline underline-offset-4">bespoke research</a>
        </li>
        <li><a href="/advisory" class="underline underline-offset-4">advisory support</a></li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
        This architecture is designed to make concepts reusable, assumptions explicit, and
        decisions easier to stress-test.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-neutral-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight mb-4">
        Work with Autonomy Bridge
      </h2>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800">
        For retained support, see <a href="/advisory" class="underline underline-offset-4">Advisory</a>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-base md:text-[17px] leading-8 text-neutral-800 mt-4">
        For custom scoped work, see <a href="/bespoke-research" class="underline underline-offset-4">Bespoke Research</a>.
      </p>
    </section>
  </article>
</MainLayout>
